# revora-frontend

- Next.js 16 App Router + TypeScript
- Admin UI uses **shadcn/ui**, not Polaris web components
- DB: Turso/libSQL via Drizzle (`src/db/schema.ts`, `src/db/index.ts`)
- Shopify auth: `@shopify/shopify-api`, sessions in Turso, embedded app via App Bridge
- Extension APIs under `app/api/extension/*` — use `extensionJsonResponse` + CORS helpers
- App base URL: prefer `HOST` env from Shopify CLI (`lib/extension/app-url.ts`)
- Run locally: `shopify app dev` from `revora-frontend/`